OL,3,CHow will new VAR rules affect England
OL,4,Cin the 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FThe International Football Association
OL,7,FBoard (IFAB) has approved new Video
OL,8,FAssistant Referee (VAR) protocol ahead
OL,9,Fof the 2026 World Cup and the changes
OL,10,Fcould impact how England play in the
OL,11,Fmen's tournament over the summer.
OL,13,FThe new measures will give VAR a
OL,14,Fbigger role in matches and could lead
OL,15,Fto more players being penalised.
OL,17,FITV News explains what the new rules
OL,18,Fare and how they could change the
OL,19,Fteam's gameplay.
OL,21,FHow will VAR be used in the World Cup?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
