OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780326668
OL,3,CHow will new VAR rules affect England
OL,4,Cin the 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FThe IFAB said in a statement that it
OL,7,Fhas approved a clarification to the
OL,8,FVAR protocol.
OL,10,FIt specifically covers "clear offences
OL,11,Fcommitted by the attacking team before
OL,12,Fthe ball is in play at a corner kick
OL,13,For free kick that have a direct impact
OL,14,Fon a goal, penalty kick, or
OL,15,Fdisciplinary sanction".
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
