OL,3,CHow will new VAR rules affect England
OL,4,Cin the 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FMeasures that have changed ahead of
OL,7,Fthe World Cup include:
OL,9,FAs with previous protocols, the VAR
OL,10,Fwill be able to recommend on-field
OL,11,Freviews and then disciplinary action
OL,12,Fcan be taken by the referee.
OL,14,FHow will England be impacted?
OL,16,FFormer top official Pierluigi Collina,
OL,17,Fnow FIFA's chief refereeing officer
OL,18,Fand chairman of the FIFA referees
OL,19,Fcommittee, used an England goal in
OL,20,FMarch as an example of what would no
OL,21,Flonger be allowed under the new rules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
