PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780326668
OL,3,CHow will new VAR rules affect England
OL,4,Cin the 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FCollina argued that England's goal in
OL,7,Ftheir 1-1 friendly against Uruguay
OL,8,Fshould not have stood, as midfielder
OL,9,FAdam Wharton made a clear block to
OL,10,Fprevent defender Jose Maria Gimenez
OL,11,Ffrom challenging for the ball shortly
OL,12,Fbefore the corner was taken.
OL,14,F"We are convinced that this goal
OL,15,Fcannot stand, it is completely
OL,16,Funfair..." Collina said. "If a foul is
OL,17,Fcommitted just before the ball is in
OL,18,Fplay, we are convinced that nobody can
OL,19,Fobject to something."
