OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780326668
OL,3,CHow will new VAR rules affect England
OL,4,Cin the 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FEngland boss Thomas Tuchel suggested
OL,7,Fearlier in the year that he thought
OL,8,Fset-pieces, such as corner kicks, free
OL,9,Fkicks and throw-ins, could help the
OL,10,Fteam win the World Cup, but now the
OL,11,Fnew rules might cause him to rethink
OL,12,Fhow the team will play.
OL,14,FWhy are the rules changing now?
OL,16,FIFAB has said the new measures are
OL,17,Fdesigned to "enhance match tempo" and
OL,18,F"reduce time-wasting" across games.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
