OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780326668
OL,3,CHow will new VAR rules affect England
OL,4,Cin the 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FThey come into force ahead of the
OL,7,FWorld Cup, which starts on June 11,
OL,8,Fand "respond directly to calls from
OL,9,Fstakeholders across the football
OL,10,Fcommunity", IFAB said.
OL,12,FAlmost all football matches adhere to
OL,13,Fthe IFAB rules, which are known as the
OL,14,FLaws of the Game.
